text: Musik, dans & party 11, also known as Vågar du så vågar jag, is a 1996 Sten & Stanley studio album.Information at Svensk mediedatabasInformation at Sten & Stanley's website The album received a Grammis Award in the "Dansband of the Year" category. ==Track listing== #"Vågar du så vågar jag" (T.
